{"tid":2122192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近日推出D抗疫方法係廢做, 港共係唔係想加速爆發?","createTime":"2020-07-24T00:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T02:18:08.000Z","uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfea45bb64dba6646a02e29a4e85354146483ac","tid":2122192,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T00:40:13.000Z","msg":"因應本地中招個䅁已達3位數字(琴日, 確診為118宗, 初步確診約為80多, 婆仔數即係200宗喇, 又破新高, 吊佢!), <br />\n近日, 陳肇(毛)始公佈推出D抗疫方法根本就係廢做:<br />\n1) 強制執行室內及乘車要帶口罩, 一來, 無帶的人係有, 但真係極少數, 二來, 執法極難(針對示威者例外)。<br />\n2) 停晚市堂食, 更被批係做一半, 唔做另一半!<br />\n3) D醫學專家日日靠各媒體向港共提水, 但港共只聽佢想聽, 照做佢想做!<br />\n4) 已實行的抗疫方法, 毫無走前幾步的意願, 只有見步行步之勢!<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">港共係唔係想加速爆發?</span></span>"},{"pid":"3430e46695610898f64b35f9c9916cee1e158c2e","tid":2122192,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n有元朗街坊見到大陸人一路行街一路播毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121428</a>"},{"pid":"0230d695eeaf10546fed02f40b9cdde2c903bed4","tid":2122192,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3430e46695610898f64b35f9c9916cee1e158c2e","tid":2122192,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n有元朗街坊見到大陸人一路行街一路播毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121428</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:01:07.000Z","msg":"劍指8月37日?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab374fd3c1550fabeb7169a2970f4788938b17aa","tid":2122192,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0230d695eeaf10546fed02f40b9cdde2c903bed4","tid":2122192,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"